feat(web): vision doc + Instant Workspace Replay

- Add /docs/vision — the "Agentic Sovereign Layer" vision page with the
  Umbrella-vs-Bankr swarm comparison table and the three-pillar narrative.
  Link it from the Getting Started section of the docs sidebar.
- New lib/recent-launches: localStorage-backed store for pending Forge
  launches with a usePendingLaunches hook that stays in sync across tabs.
- New LaunchReplayPanel component mounted above the DAG in /app/workspace.
  Shows every pending launch as an Initializing/Forging/Ready/Failed card
  and subscribes to Supabase Realtime so launches flip to Ready the moment
  the generated_hooks row lands.
- Forge wizard handleSubmit now stashes an optimistic pending launch and
  immediately routes the user to /app/workspace. The /api/v1/forge/launch
  POST continues in the background and resolves the card to Ready (or
  Failed) when it returns.
